<p>Este elenco conta tamb\xE9m com grandes nomes do cinema, como <strong>Don Cheadle</strong> (\u201CAvengers\u201D e \u201CHotel Rwanda\u201D), <strong>Khris Davis</strong> (\u201CJudas e o Messias Negro\u201D) e <strong>Sonequa Martin-Green</strong> (\u201CThe Walking Dead\u201D e \u201CStar Trek: Discovery\u201D). Entre os jogadores da NBA, da WNBA e de outras modalidades teremos: <strong>Klay Thompson</strong>, <strong>Anthony Davis</strong>, <strong>Damian Lillard</strong>, <strong>Chris Paul</strong>, <strong>Draymond Green</strong>, <strong>Kyle Kuzma</strong>, <strong>Diana Taurasi</strong>, <strong>Nneka Ogwumike</strong> e <strong>Chiney Ogwumike</strong>.</p>
